NK011(da)006:0: bo d+hi tsit+ta +aahh+aum a yu she sid+d+hi h+aum +aah h+aum /
NK011(da)006:1: ye shes khro bo h+aum k+aa ra //
NK011(da)006:2: sgra 'byin yum dang mnyam par sbyor //
NK011(da)006:3: gnyis su med pa'i byang sems kyis //
NK011(da)006:4: spyi nas bstim nas dbang bskur zhing //
NK011(da)006:5: lce yi steng du bzhag pa yis //
NK011(da)006:6: h+aum k+aa ra yab yum dngos grub sbyin //
NK011(da)006:8: ye shes khro bo rnam par rgyal //
NK011(da)006:9: snyems ma yum dang mnyam par sbyor //
NK011(da)006:10: gnyis su spyi nas lce yi rnam rgyal bo d+hi tsit+ta h+aum /
NK011(da)006:11: ye shes khro bo dbyug sngon can //
NK011(da)006:12: sder mo gnyis su spyi nas lce yi dbyug sngon bo d+hi tsit+ta h+aum /
NK011(da)006:13: ye shes khro bo gshin rje gshed //
NK011(da)006:14: dur khrod ma gnyis su spyi nas lce yi gshin
NK011(da)006:15: rje bo d+hi tsit+ta h+aum ye shes khro bo mi
NK011(da)006:16: g.yo ba // gtun khung gnyis su spyi nas lce yi mi g.yo bo d+hi tsit+ta h+aum /
NK011(da)006:17: ye shes khro bo rta mgrin rgyal //
NK011(da)006:18: gtum mo gnyis su spyi nas lce yi rta mgrin bo d+hi tsit+ta h+aum /
NK011(da)006:19: ye shes khro bo 'dod pa'i rgyal //
NK011(da)006:20: mda' snyems gnyis su spyi nas lce yi 'dod rgyal bo d+hi tsit+ta h+aum /
NK011(da)006:21: ye shes khro bo bdud rtsi 'khyil //
NK011(da)006:22: rlung 'byin gnyis su spyi nas lce yi bdud rtsi bo d+hi tsit+ta h+aum /
NK011(da)006:23: ye shes khro bo khams gsum rgyal //
NK011(da)006:24: gsod byed gnyis su spyi nas lce yi khams gsum bo d+hi tsit+ta h+aum /
NK011(da)006:25: ye shes khro bo stobs po che //
NK011(da)006:26: bskyod byed gnyis su spyi nas lce yi stobs chen bo d+hi tsit+ta sogs //
